<inglise>(3) The Estonian Health Insurance Fund has the right to claim compensation instead of the injured party for damage to health or a bodily injury caused by a public authority, to the extent of the medical insurance benefit and medical treatment expenses paid to the injured party by the Estonian Health Insurance Fund. </inglise>
