<eesti>Kaitsev&auml;elase varaline vastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Proprietary liability of members of Defence Forces </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaitsev&auml;elane on kohustatud h&uuml;vitama riigile s&uuml;&uuml;liselt teenistuskohustuste rikkumisega tekitatud kahju. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A member of the Defence Forces is required to compensate to the state for damage wrongfully caused as a result of a breach of duties. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Riigile kaitsev&auml;elase poolt tekitatud kahju on ka riigi poolt makstud h&uuml;vitis kaitsev&auml;elase teenistuskohustuste rikkumisega kolmandale isikule tekitatud kahju eest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Compensation paid by the state for damage caused to a third party as a result of a breach of duties by a member of the Defence Forces is also damage caused by a member of the Defence Forces. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaitsev&auml;elase poolt riigile tekitatud kahju eest v&auml;ljam&otilde;istetava h&uuml;vitise suuruse kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramisel ning kahju h&uuml;vitamise korra osas kohaldatakse avaliku teenistuse seaduses ametniku varalist vastutust reguleerivaid s&auml;tteid. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon determining the amount of compensation ordered to be paid for damage caused to the state by a member of the Defence Forces and with regard to the procedure for compensation for damage, provisions of the Public Service Act which regulate the proprietary liability of officials apply. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kahju h&uuml;vitamiseks teeb kaitsev&auml;elasele ettepaneku ja p&ouml;&ouml;rdub halduskohtu poole h&uuml;vitise v&auml;ljam&otilde;istmiseks kaitsev&auml;elase teenistust korraldav &uuml;lem. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The commanding officer who regulates the service of a member of the Defence Forces shall make a proposal to the member of the Defence Forces to compensate for damage and shall have recourse to an administrative court for the order of payment of compensation. </inglise>
